pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `bf0e388` to `9b4d4bb`.
Commits
  • 9b4d4bb Change CMake files to support macos on Apple Silicon (#1034)
  • 1009721 Update Doxygen file (#1046)
  • c4122ec Added macOS formatting rules for exported arm assembly symbols (#1042)
  • 706cc89 removing BIKE R2 from README (#1047)
  • f3caccf Removing default algs (#1044)
  • 21dcba4 Remove old versions of BIKE (#1045)
  • c071b01 Sike June updates (#1028)
  • a822f0e PQClean / NTRU Prime update (#1039)
  • d9fb4e0 Add OQS_PERMIT_UNSUPPORTED_ARCHITECTURE flag (#1021)
  • 7a5097d Make BIKE compile for different CMake versions when AVX512 is used (#1033)
